<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CareBridge’07 | Dynamic Global Ltd</title>
    <style>
        /* Premium Reset & Typography */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { background-color: #0B132B; color: #FFFFFF; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        /* Navigation Hub */
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 25px 10%; background: rgba(11, 19, 43, 0.95); position: fixed; width: 100%; top: 0; z-index: 1000; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
        .logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #FFFFFF; }
        .logo span { color: #FFB703; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; }
        .nav-links li { margin-left: 35px; }
        .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #BDC3C7; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: color 0.3s; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: #FFB703; }
        
        /* Premium Hero Banner Section */
        .hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 10%; background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(29, 38, 113, 0.4), #0B132B); padding-top: 80px; }
        .hero-content { max-width: 800px; }
        .tagline { color: #FFB703; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h1 { font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #FFFFFF; }
        h1 span { display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 40px; font-weight: 300; margin-top: 5px; }
        p { font-size: 18px; color: #AFB6C5; margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 650px; }
        
        /* Action Call Buttons */
        .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 16px 35px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; text-align: center; }
        .btn-primary { background-color: #FFB703; color: #0B132B; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: #E09F00; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .btn-secondary { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #FFFFFF; }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); transform: translateY(-2px); }        /* Institutional Services Section */
        .section-padding { padding: 100px 10%; }
        .section-title { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
        .section-subtitle { color: #FFB703; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        
        .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1max)); gap: 30px; }
        .service-card { background: #1C2541; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.4); }
        .service-icon { font-size: 24px; color: #FFB703; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .service-card h3 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
        .service-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #AFB6C5; margin-bottom: 0; }

        /* GDI Metrics Matrix Section */
        .gdi-section { background-color: #060B18; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        .matrix-container { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .matrix-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: #1C2541; padding: 25px 35px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #FFB703; }
        .matrix-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
        .matrix-dim { font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: #FFB703; font-weight: 600; }
        .matrix-name { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #FFFFFF; }
        .matrix-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #AFB6C5; max-width: 600px; }
        .matrix-weight { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #FFFFFF; opacity: 0.9; font-family: monospace; }

        /* Mobile Optimization overrides */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 20px 5%; }
            .nav-links { display: none; } /* Kept simple for mobile step-by-step */
            .hero { padding: 0 5%; padding-top: 100px; }
            h1 { font-size: 36px; }
            h1 span { font-size: 26px; }
            .section-padding { padding: 70px 5%; }
            .matrix-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; padding: 20px; }
            .matrix-weight { align-self: flex-end; font-size: 24px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">CAREBRIDGE<span>’07</span></div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#services">Framework Matrix</a></li>
            <li><a href="#gdi">GDI Index Architecture</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="tagline">Dynamic Global Ltd // Care Intelligence Ecosystem</div>
            <h1>Transforming Human Dignity into Auditable <span>Care Governance Metrics.</span></h1>
            <p>We challenge the traditional vulnerabilities of donor-dependent welfare models by engineering data-driven, shock-responsive protection systems tailored for emerging economies.</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary">Institutional Services</a>
                <a href="#gdi" class="btn btn-secondary">The GDI Engine</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="section-padding">
        <h2 class="section-title">Institutional Capabilities</h2>
        <div class="section-subtitle">B2G & B2B Care Governance Operations</div>
        
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Metric-Driven Social Protection Auditing</h3>
                <p>Deploying specialized compliance frameworks that convert qualitative social development interventions into verifiable, audit-ready field data for development finance banks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🌐</div>
                <h3>Decentralized Case Management Systems</h3>
                <p>Architecting multi-tier cloud interfaces for public authorities to monitor regional vulnerabilities, deploy resources, and minimize intervention latency in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🛡️</div>
                <h3>MHPSS & Protection Systems</h3>
                <p>Engineering robust, legally aligned behavioral intervention protocols, tracking safety infrastructure metrics, and designing structural frameworks against societal vulnerability.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gdi" class="section-padding gdi-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Geriatric Dignity Index Matrix</h2>
        <div class="section-subtitle">Weighted Linear Aggregation Architecture</div>
        
        <div class="matrix-container">
            <div class="matrix-row">
                <div class="matrix-info">
                    <span class="matrix-dim">Dimension One (D1)</span>
                    <span class="matrix-name">Structural Autonomy</span>
                    <span class="matrix-desc">Calculates self-determination tracking, dietary choice participation, and independent environmental control capacity.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="matrix-weight">w = 0.25</div>
            </div>
            <div class="matrix-row">
                <div class="matrix-info">
                    <span class="matrix-dim">Dimension Two (D2)</span>
                    <span class="matrix-name">Executive Agency</span>
                    <span class="matrix-desc">Measures financial asset visibility, healthcare proxy documentation, and legal status validation.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="matrix-weight">w = 0.20</div>
            </div>
            <div class="matrix-row">
                <div class="matrix-info">
                    <span class="matrix-dim">Dimension Three (D3)</span>
                    <span class="matrix-name">Psychosocial Legacy</span>
                    <span class="matrix-desc">Tracks historical data archival, identity preservation assets, and knowledge transmission matrices.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="matrix-weight">w = 0.25</div>
            </div>
            <div class="matrix-row">
                <div class="matrix-info">
                    <span class="matrix-dim">Dimension Four (D4)</span>
                    <span class="matrix-name">Biophysical Security</span>
                    <span class="matrix-desc">Evaluates safety infrastructure installation, environmental risk exposure, and exploitation screenings.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="matrix-weight">w = 0.15</div>
            </div>
            <div class="matrix-row">
                <div class="matrix-info">
                    <span class="matrix-dim">Dimension Five (D5)</span>
                    <span class="matrix-name">Communitarian Participation</span>
                    <span class="matrix-desc">Quantifies localized engagement frequencies, intergenerational interactions, and social asset accessibility.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="matrix-weight">w = 0.15</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
